### Health and Service Status
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### Prometheus Performance Metrics
GET http://localhost:3000/metrics

### Login (Supports both JSON body and HTTP Basic Auth)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Secure Endpoint Test (Requires JWT from Login)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/secure-ping
Authorization: Bearer <YOUR_TOKEN_HERE>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "data": "Hello World"
}

### Standard Single UI Calculation (Requires JWT)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/calculations/calculate
Authorization: Bearer <YOUR_TOKEN_HERE>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "age": 30,
  "policy_term": 20,
  "premium_payment_term": 15,
  "premium_amount": 50000
}

### Scalable Bulk Calculation Mechanism (Requires JWT)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/bulk/upload
Authorization: Bearer <YOUR_TOKEN_HERE>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "calculations": [
    {
      "product_id": "01000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
      "age": 40,
      "policy_term": 15,
      "premium_payment_term": 10,
      "premium_amount": 100000
    },
    {
      "product_id": "02000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
      "age": 25,
      "policy_term": 30,
      "premium_payment_term": 30,
      "premium_amount": 25000
    }
  ]
}
